Author: ComputerGenie 游놊游낖游닉#7004
Content:
`341 seconds until eligible`
means that it's 341 seconds until your "earliest" eligible UTXO __can__ be attempted to be staked

Author: ComputerGenie 游놊游낖游닉#7004
Content: any CPU cycles you see being used before then are the process by which it keeps checking if you have anything else available to stake sooner
